  assumes "trading_strategy pf"
and "portfolio pf"
and "borel_adapt_stoch_proc F (prices Mkt asset)"
and "support_adapt Mkt pf"
shows "trading_strategy (self_finance Mkt v pf asset)" unfolding self_finance_def
